# Code Style Conventions

## General

- Keep lines under 90 columns

## JavaScript / TypeScript

- Always use function definitions instead of arrow functions

```typescript
// ✅ Good
function handleClick(event) {
  // ...
}

// ❌ Bad
const handleClick = (event) => {
  // ...
}
```

## Shell Scripts

- Always use the env form of the shebang

```bash
# ✅ Good
#!/usr/bin/env bash

# ❌ Bad
#!/bin/bash
```
